flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New/updated near-term demand segmentation and short-term forecast roll produced (scheduled or delta) indicating changes to SKU-level demand priority or shape within the next 0-14 day horizon.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest segmentation, short-term forecast, inventory, capacity and shortage signals]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS + Subject Areas - Validate and surface consolidated short-horizon demand and constraints]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder (Rules + Remote Functions) - Compute optimized sequencing and line allocation plan using deterministic rules and business constraints}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions (ERP/MES writeback) + Process Builder - Execute allocations and sequencing updates to execution systems and propagate shortages]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle (Action Item) + Notification - Notify production planners and create action items for exceptions/overrides]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screens + Subject Areas (dashboard) - Review outcomes and surface KPIs to planners and supply chain ops]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Short-term alignment of Plan and Make: reduced SKU stockouts and excess, improved service levels for prioritized demand segments, fewer emergency expediting events, and measurable COGS improvement from more efficient line utilization and fewer rush logistics.]
  N3 -->|Capacity constraints prevent satisfyi...| B1[Create CWB Lifecycle exception routing to planner team with recommended expediting and order re-prioritization; flag orders for Kinaxis escalation]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop approval for overtime/expedite; Kinaxis propagates shortage and shipping adjustments to minimize service impact]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Forecast uncertainty or segmentation ...| B2[Trigger wait node + request additional confirmatory signals (shorter horizon forecasts or recent sales pull-in) and surface alternative conservative sequencing options]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Defer automatic heavy reallocation; present safe fallback plan to avoid overreaction and protect COGS]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|MES/ERP writeback fails or returns co...| B3[Rollback transaction in Process Builder, generate Action Item via CWB Lifecycle for manual resolution and re-run pre-flight validations]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Safe failure mode preventing invalid orders; planners resolve root cause and reapply sequencing with corrected data]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]